{"tid":2417242,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都中意佢哋是但一個: 菅田將暉，佐藤健，綾野剛，柄本佑","createTime":"2021-02-21T17:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T00:47:53.000Z","uid":174979,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3f038f78d22e99e9fc43e248e6b815be9ba287","tid":2417242,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"最近搵佢哋啲日綜片睇越嚟越中意佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有無啲蘇打嘅日綜係好笑推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話山崎賢人係100分外表同0分內在笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近睇咗佢同柄本佑上007，佢兩個超好笑，柄本更加係超好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n砂糖好中意睇佢玩game，睇哂佢同山田孝之仲有其他藝人玩狼人殺嘅片好好笑好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綾野剛係之前睇Miu404之後入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵佢嘅日綜睇，人間觀察做攝影師嗰集佢真係好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他佢哋上日綜嘅推薦？<br />\n或者好笑日綜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw搵片睇嗰陣睇到有人剪咗小栗旬揮手片段合輯，笑到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedaffbb5ef26f9d2e1928b6d728c3469be54fd5","tid":2417242,"uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"中意炳本時生"},{"pid":"f39492f68881824e197da7666e3aa4d29c11cec8","tid":2417242,"uid":24457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:27:20.000Z","msg":"鍾意聽菅田將暉啲歌 算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 